name: Sydney
profile:
A talented ninja with the nickname "Swordbreaker".
He is a taciturn young man who wields a variety of ninjutsu and katanas.

name: Rachel
profile:
An armed priest who has mastered healing miracles and fist-fighting techniques.
She is a determined and brave girl who can fight to protect someone.

name: Patrick
profile:
A holy knight from the Empire. He specializes in spears and self-buffs.
He is an honest and quiet man, but he also has the courage to charge alone in battle.

name: Grace
profile:
A stealth who specializes in sorcery and archery. He is good at supporting from the rear guard.
She's a good-natured, big-sister woman, but her weak point is that she's weak to alcohol.

name: Gilbert
profile:
A heavy warrior who wields a huge battle ax with ease. As avant-garde as it looks.
He is good at debuff attacks and sees Sydney as his rival.

name: Ellen
profile:
A genius at the Magic Academy who can handle various types of magic by using different magic books.
She plays a bewitching adult woman, but she is actually a maiden who falls in love.

name: Anastasia
profile:
A traveling dancer who fights with a dagger. Specialize in supporting allies.
Raises the abilities of nearby allies through various dances.

name: Rufus
profile:
An engineer who uses a new weapon called a magic gun. He specializes in special attacks.
He is not good at socializing, but when it comes to fighting, he displays his genius skills.

name: Reid
profile:
A hero who appears in many stories.
For 3 turns, he fights with automatic actions.
